title: Shaun O'Hara, Worst ice cream flavors & Travis Kelce
itunes:title: Shaun O'Hara, Worst ice cream flavors & Travis Kelce
description:
NFL Network's Shaun O'Hara and Dave Dameshek kibbitz in Studio 66 about the Dolphins' old baggage (3:00), Browns vs Giants preseason match up, including answering the question 'was Baker Mayfield the right No. 1 overall pick' (14:00), Shaun's least favorite ice cream flavor (22:25), would the AFC East be worst division in NFL history without Tom Brady (30:50) and lastly, Dave interviews Kansas City Chiefs' tight end, Travis Kelce (40:30).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
